heading: How many cows are in each EU country?
subheading: Across EU countries the numbers vary heavily
extraInfoText_DE: Route 99 leads from the northern Israeli city of Kiryat Shmona via Majdal Shams, a town inhabited by Syrian Druze directly on Mount Hermon, to the Israeli-occupied Golan Heights. Until a few weeks ago, this stretch was a restricted military area. It runs along the border with Lebanon and up to the border with Syria. From here, the terrorist militia Hezbollah fired most of its rockets and drones.
